Audio-Assault GrindMachine v1.2 VST AU RTAS WiN OSX RETAiL







Grind Machine is the ultimate metal tone monster.
No need to tweak, just plug Grind Machine into your track and enjoy instant mix ready tones that cut through your mix effortlessly.

Grind Machine keeps it simple, using any of it's 12 amplifiers and 20 cabinets it gives you over 240 kick-ass sounding rig variations, leaving you to focus on the songwriting process and save time on your mix.

Grind Machine also includes DJENTBOX, an overdrive pedal that makes low tunings sound tighter and more in your face!

High quality sound, ultra-low CPU usage and a simple to use interface make Grind Machine one of the most useful tools for Metal songwriters, musicians and producers everywhere
